  "3187880": {
    "name": "杀手寓言 Manga Build Roguelike",
    "steam_appid": 3187880,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《杀手寓言 Manga Build Roguelike》是一款将漫画、战术解谜与Roguelike元素完美融合的游戏，玩家可通过灵活的思维、精密的策略，以及以像素画风格呈现的角色时尚动作，尽享游戏乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.avif?t=1763363287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras_big/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.webp?t=1763363287 width=1560 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/87e83bf3f11865987643b8f6f8b9c85a.avif?t=1763363287\" width=1280 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/c714a543819c5246e8a14adefdd734e8.poster.avif?t=1763363287\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/c714a543819c5246e8a14adefdd734e8.webm?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/c714a543819c5246e8a14adefdd734e8.mp4?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集漫画的“格子”并将其配置在页面上进行战斗的【漫画 × 战术解谜 × Roguelike】的全新玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・每回合分配的“格子”放置到页面上即为指令输入 <br>・“格子”会从页面的右上角向左下角依次触发 <br>・“格子”的形状与触发顺序是战斗的关键 <br>・考验的是玩家的“智慧与巧思”。根据局势配置“格子”，拼出最优的页面，将敌人击飞！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.avif?t=1763363287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras_big/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.webp?t=1763363287 width=1560 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/04c377948fe546e8782435d9f66dca6e.avif?t=1763363287\" width=1275 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/a5b6087877ca757b87154e542c6cefc8.poster.avif?t=1763363287\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/a5b6087877ca757b87154e542c6cefc8.webm?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/a5b6087877ca757b87154e542c6cefc8.mp4?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由三位个性鲜明的角色带来截然不同的体验</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・明：杀戮天才。精通打击与枪击，正面击溃敌人！ <br>・洋子：明的搭档。以敏捷的步伐迷惑敌人，从背后猛烈一击！ <br>・铃木：冷酷的杀手。运用枪击、陷阱与减益，以技术手段将敌人逼入绝境！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.avif?t=1763363287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras_big/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.webp?t=1763363287 width=1560 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/1866e5ee1eb5ea4f7d62f4b70da5e22b.avif?t=1763363287\" width=1280 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>受到伤害 = 下一回合的行动限制。为了在限制回合内消灭敌人，需要进行策略思考</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・战斗中受到的伤害会转化为“下一回合可使用的页面破损” <br>・破损的位置无法放置“格子”，因此受到伤害 = 下一回合的行动限制 <br>・战斗的通关条件是“在限制回合内消灭敌人” <br>・是冒险进攻，还是稳固防守？一切取决于你的战略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.avif?t=1763363287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras_big/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.webp?t=1763363287 width=1560 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/026eb292dba094cd50d35d62b460506e.avif?t=1763363287\" width=1280 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/2e1d3d2b277c2c8cd335efb94b4ca436.poster.avif?t=1763363287\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/2e1d3d2b277c2c8cd335efb94b4ca436.webm?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/2e1d3d2b277c2c8cd335efb94b4ca436.mp4?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在依靠“智慧与巧思”的紧张战斗间隙，还会出现一些能让人稍作喘息的、带有荒诞色彩的小游戏事件。如果在小游戏中获得高分，就有机会获得强大的“格子”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.avif?t=1763363287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras_big/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.webp?t=1763363287 width=1560 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/9d0acbe34c25202cef6aef1fc04b6eef.avif?t=1763363287\" width=1280 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了满足那些渴望不断追求自身“智慧与巧思”的用户，我们特别准备了“解谜模式”。 <br>利用给定的“格子”，在一页之内将敌人全部击败。 <br>（高难度的谜题需要多少思考与时间来完成，连开发者也不清楚。但请放心，一定有答案，请不要放弃，坚持下去！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.avif?t=1763363287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras_big/532ba61f2311a4cab6890f59d6aef86d.webp?t=1763363287 width=1560 height=208 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/5b674110538f54eaa802c3c17c8e2ab4.avif?t=1763363287\" width=1280 height=380 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/a870e6a6e48ddc9fbc524563338a6254.poster.avif?t=1763363287\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/a870e6a6e48ddc9fbc524563338a6254.webm?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187880/extras/a870e6a6e48ddc9fbc524563338a6254.mp4?t=1763363287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >说到《杀手寓言》，这个男人绝不能缺席。<br>花花公子河合为了追求在酒吧出现的美女洋子，决定用“酒”为赌注来一决胜负。<br>这位天真、鲁莽又愚蠢的男人，能否在“醉酒女王”洋子面前展现自己帅气的一面呢——？</p>",
